<section xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xml:id="EnablePostfix" version="5.0">
 <title xml:id="SysMgmtServices">Enable Postfix</title>
 <para>
  The postfix daemon is responsible for local mail delivery, and is
  essential to many maintenance and notification activities. It is
  recommended that this service always be on.
 </para>
